<node CREATED="1282098804538" ID="ID_93234944" MODIFIED="1282099127118" TEXT="&gt;&gt;&gt; from urllib import urlencode&#xa;&gt;&gt;&gt; import urllib2&#xa;&gt;&gt;&gt; def foo(arg):&#xa;...     x = 1&#xa;...     print locals()&#xa;...     locals()[&apos;x&apos;] = 2&#xa;...     print locals()&#xa;... &#xa;&gt;&gt;&gt; y = 1&#xa;&gt;&gt;&gt; foo(7)&#xa;{&apos;x&apos;: 1, &apos;arg&apos;: 7}&#xa;{&apos;x&apos;: 1, &apos;arg&apos;: 7} &lt;-- &#x8b8a;&#x66f4;&#x8907;&#x672c;&#x6c92;&#x6709;&#x7528;&#xa;&gt;&gt;&gt; print globals()&#xa;{&apos;urlencode&apos;: &lt;function urlencode at 0x7f42a6a7e9b0&gt;, &apos;__builtins__&apos;: &lt;module &apos;__builtin__&apos; (built-in)&gt;, &apos;urllib2&apos;: &lt;module &apos;urllib2&apos; from &apos;/usr/lib/python2.6/urllib2.pyc&apos;&gt;, &apos;__package__&apos;: None, &apos;y&apos;: 1, &apos;__name__&apos;: &apos;__main__&apos;, &apos;foo&apos;: &lt;function foo at 0x7f42a6b409b0&gt;, &apos;__doc__&apos;: None}&#xa;&gt;&gt;&gt; globals()[&apos;y&apos;] = 2&#xa;&gt;&gt;&gt; globals()[&apos;x&apos;] = 9999&#xa;&gt;&gt;&gt; print x, y&#xa;9999 2             &lt;-- &#x771f;&#x7684;&#x88ab;&#x4fee;&#x6539;&#x4e86;!!&#xa;"/>
