<node CREATED="1299037413573" ID="ID_360586477" MODIFIED="1299037420059" TEXT="If the optional `sizehint` argument is present, instead of reading up to EOF, whole lines totalling approximately `sizehint` bytes (possibly after rounding up to an internal buffer size) are read."/>
