<node CREATED="1285813416808" ID="ID_1437249081" MODIFIED="1285813489159" TEXT="Fairly portable uname interface. Returns a tuple of strings `(system, node, release, version, machine, processor)` identifying the underlying platform. Entries which cannot be determined are set to `&apos;&apos;`."/>
